gov.va.med.srcalc.domain.variable

Interface Variable

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    DiscreteVariable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractNumericalVariable, AbstractVariable, BooleanVariable, DiscreteNumericalVariable, MultiSelectVariable, NumericalVariable, ProcedureVariable

    public interface Variable
    A model variable. Just the variable, does not store an inputted value.

    • Method Detail

      • getKey

        java.lang.String getKey()
        Returns a key which should be unique among all Variables. Ideally should be alphanumeric, though this isn't enforced.

      • getDisplayName

        java.lang.String getDisplayName()
        Returns a String suitable for display to humans. Will be no longer than DISPLAY_NAME_MAX.

      • getGroup

        VariableGroup getGroup()
        Returns the VariableGroup for this Variable. Never null.

      • getHelpText

        java.lang.String getHelpText()

      • getRetrievalKey

        java.lang.Integer getRetrievalKey()
        Returns a key that is used to translate vista retrieved values to variable keys. Retrieval keys do not have to be unique.

      • getRetrievalDateString

        java.lang.String getRetrievalDateString()
        Should not be persisted to the database, as the retrieval date comes from Vista.

      • setRetrievalDateString

        void setRetrievalDateString(java.lang.String retrievalDateString)

        Accepts the given VariableVisitor.
        Throws:
        java.lang.Exception - if the VariableVisitor throws an Exception
